                <div class="col-lg-10">
                    <div class="pp-policy-card card shadow-sm border-0">
                        <div class="card-body p-4 p-md-5">
                            
                            <!-- Introduction -->
                            <section class="mb-5">
                                <h2 class="h3 mb-3 pp-section-title">1. Introduction</h2>
                                <p>At IVF Fertility Clinic, we understand the sensitivity of your personal and medical information. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, disclose, and protect your information when you use our services. We adhere to all applicable healthcare privacy laws, including HIPAA, to ensure your data remains confidential and secure.</p>
                            </section>

                            <!-- Information We Collect -->
                            <section class="mb-5">
                                <h2 class="h3 mb-3 pp-section-title">2. Information We Collect</h2>
                                <p>We collect various types of information to provide you with quality fertility care:
                                    <br>
                               
                                    Personal Details Name, date of birth, address, contact information, insurance details, and government-issued identification numbers.
                                    Medical Information Medical history, fertility test results, treatment plans, medication records, and other health-related data necessary for your care.</p>
                                
                            </section>

                            <!-- How We Use Your Information -->
                            <section class="mb-5">
                                <h2 class="h3 mb-3 pp-section-title">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
                                <p>Your information is used exclusively for purposes related to your care and our clinic operations:<br>
                               
                                   Appointment Scheduling To manage your appointments, send reminders, and coordinate your care.
