                                   Communication Purposes To respond to your inquiries, provide test results, share educational materials, and send important clinic updates.</p>
                                
                            </section>

                            <!-- Data Protection & Security -->
                            <section class="mb-5">
                                <h2 class="h3 mb-3 pp-section-title">4. Data Protection & Security</h2>
                                <p>We implement comprehensive security measures to protect your information:<br>
                               
                                   Encrypted electronic medical records system with access controls and audit trails
                                   Secure physical storage for paper records in locked, access-controlled areas
