                                    Essential Cookies Required for the website to function properly, such as maintaining your session security.
                                    Analytics Cookies Help us understand how visitors use our site, allowing us to improve its functionality and content.
                                    Preference Cookies Remember your settings and preferences for future visits.</p>
                            </section>

                            <!-- Third-Party Sharing -->
                            <section class="mb-5">
                                <h2 class="h3 mb-3 pp-section-title">6. Third-Party Sharing</h2>
                                <p>We may share your information with third parties only in specific circumstances:<br>
                               
                                   With other healthcare providers involved in your treatment (with your consent)
                                   With insurance companies for billing and authorization purposes
                                   With accredited laboratories for diagnostic testing
                                   When required by law (e.g., public health reporting, legal proceedings)
                                   For business operations (e.g., IT support, billing services) under strict confidentiality agreements.</p>
                            </section>

                            <!-- Patient Rights -->
                            <section class="mb-5">
                                <h2 class="h3 mb-3 pp-section-title">7. Patient Rights</h2>
                                <p>You have specific rights regarding your health information:<br>
                               
                                   Access to Data Request to view and obtain copies of your medical records.
                                   Correction of Data Request amendments to your records if you believe information is inaccurate or incomplete.
                                   Deletion Request Request deletion of your information, subject to legal and medical record-keeping requirements.
                                   Restriction of Use Request limitations on how we use or disclose your information.
                                   Confidential Communications Request alternative methods or locations for receiving communications from us.</p>
                            </section>

                            <!-- Policy Updates -->
                            <section class="mb-5">
                                <h2 class="h3 mb-3 pp-section-title">8. Policy Updates</h2>
                                <p>We may update this Privacy Policy periodically to reflect changes in our practices, technology, legal requirements, or services. When we make changes, we will update the "Last Updated" date at the bottom of this page. For significant changes, we will provide more prominent notice, which may include email notification or a notice on our website.</p>
                            </section>

                            <!-- Contact Information -->
                            <section class="mb-4">
                                <h2 class="h3 mb-3 pp-section-title">9. Contact Information</h2>
                                <p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy or our privacy practices, please contact our Privacy Officer:</p>
                                
